divs: Sighting DetailsI went outside last night to let my dogs out. When I opened the door, my attention was brought to the sky where a white round flashy orb was radiating light. As it moved northeast, it turned red and then green and took off. I stared at the sky for about 20 minutes and then saw another white light cross over. The second object didn't take off as fast as the first, but I know it was not an airplane or helicopter. There was no sound.
